<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM1.9.7">
<l>tōḷiṇai mēlunaṉ mārpiṉ mēluñ cuṭarmuṭi mēlun</l>
<l>tāḷiṇai mēlum puṉainta taṇṇan tuḻāyuṭai yammāṉ</l>
<l>kēḷiṇai yoṉṟumi lātāṉ kiḷaruñ cuṭaroḷi mūrtti</l>
<l>nāḷaṇain toṉṟu makalā ṉeṉṉuṭai nāviṉu ḷāṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The lord who has adorning cool Tulsi on [his] shoulder pair,</l>
<l>on [his] good chest on [his] glowing crown and on [his] pair of feet,</l>
<l>the one who is without any matching relative, the form of shining, glowing light,</l>
<l>he who comes near [and] does not depart every single day, he is on my tongue.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
